text: Saeid Mohammadfar (, born 2 January 1995) is an Iranian footballer who plays as a right back who currently plays for Iranian club Saipa in the Persian Gulf Pro League. ==Club career== ===Pars Jonoubi Jam=== He made his debut for Pars Jonoubi Jam in 7th fixtures of 2017–18 Iran Pro League against Saipa. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian footballers Category:Pars Jonoubi Jam players Category:Association football defenders Category:People from Qaem Shahr
